<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Work with Us - Utility Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/auth1.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1 class="logo-main" id="logo-up">Utility</h1>
        <h1 class="logo-main" id="logo-down">Genie</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="work-container">
        <h2>Join Our Team!</h2>
        <p>We are looking for skilled plumbers, electricians, and mechanics to join our platform. Hereâ€™s how you can work with us:</p>
        
        <h3>How It Works</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>**Fill Out the Application**: Complete the application form below.</li>
            <li>**Verify**: Complete our verification process.</li>
            <li>**Start Accepting Jobs**: Connect with customers needing your services.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Login</h3>
        <form action="/login?redirect=application_form" method="POST" class="login-form">
            <label for="username">Username:</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
            
            <label for="password">Password:</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
            
            <!-- Hidden input to pass redirect URL -->
            <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="application_form">

            <button type="submit">Login</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Utility Genie. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
